ectural creativity with construction precision to deliver spaces that are functional, future-ready, and aligned with client goals.\",\"additionalText\":\"By managing both design and construction within a single contract, we minimize delays, reduce risks, and ensure accountability at every stage. Our collaborative model enables faster decision-making, optimized costs, and seamless coordination—resulting in high-quality outcomes that reflect both innovation and integrity.\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"titleColor\":\"#000000\",\"subtitleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"overlay\":false}},{\"id\":\"real-estate-portfolio-1\",\"type\":\"real-estate-portfolio\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Industries\",\"subtitle\":\"Our Design and Build approach is grounded in creativity, collaboration, and precision. ensuring architectural excellence, seamless delivery, & spaces that embody both form & function for lasting impact.\",\"description\":\"Explore our diverse portfolio of completed projects that demonstrate our commitment to quality, innovation, and sustainable development.\",\"projects\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Luxury Residential Complex\",\"category\":\"Urban\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600607687939-ce8a6c25118c?w=800\",\"description\":\"A premium residential development featuring modern architecture and sustainable design.\",\"location\":\"Dubai, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"Sustainable Design\",\"Smart Home Technology\",\"Premium Amenities\"]},{\"id\":\"2\",\"title\":\"Commercial Tower\",\"category\":\"Commercial\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?w=800\",\"description\":\"State-of-the-art commercial tower with LEED certification and innovative workspace design.\",\"location\":\"Abu Dhabi, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"LEED Certified\",\"Modern Workspaces\",\"Energy Efficient\"]},{\"id\":\"3\",\"title\":\"Mixed-Use Development\",\"category\":\"Urban\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600596542815-ffad4c1539a9?w=800\",\"description\":\"Integrated mixed-use development combining retail, office, and residential spaces.\",\"location\":\"Sharjah, UAE\",\"year\":\"2022\",\"features\":[\"Mixed-Use\",\"Community Focus\",\"Retail Integration\"]},{\"id\":\"4\",\"title\":\"Sustainable Office Complex\",\"category\":\"Commercial\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497366216548-37526070297c?w=800\",\"description\":\"Eco-friendly office complex with green building certifications and modern amenities.\",\"location\":\"Dubai, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"Green Building\",\"Modern Amenities\",\"Energy Efficient\"]},{\"id\":\"5\",\"title\":\"Luxury Villa Community\",\"category\":\"Urban\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600596542815-ffad4c1539a9?w=800\",\"description\":\"Exclusive villa community with premium finishes and resort-style amenities.\",\"location\":\"Ras Al Khaimah, UAE\",\"year\":\"2022\",\"features\":[\"Premium Finishes\",\"Resort Amenities\",\"Private Security\"]},{\"id\":\"6\",\"title\":\"Urban Retail Center\",\"category\":\"Urban\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1449824913935-59a10b8d2000?w=800\",\"description\":\"Modern retail and entertainment center serving the urban community.\",\"location\":\"Fujairah, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"Retail Spaces\",\"Entertainment\",\"Urban Design\"]},{\"id\":\"7\",\"title\":\"Industrial Manufacturing Park\",\"category\":\"Industrial\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=800\",\"description\":\"Advanced industrial park with state-of-the-art manufacturing facilities and logistics support.\",\"location\":\"Ajman, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"Manufacturing Facilities\",\"Logistics Hub\",\"Sustainable Operations\"]},{\"id\":\"8\",\"title\":\"Modern University Campus\",\"category\":\"Institutional\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523050854058-8df90110c9f1?w=800\",\"description\":\"Contemporary university campus designed for innovation and academic excellence.\",\"location\":\"Abu Dhabi, UAE\",\"year\":\"2022\",\"features\":[\"Academic Facilities\",\"Research Labs\",\"Green Spaces\"]},{\"id\":\"9\",\"title\":\"Community Recreation Center\",\"category\":\"Community\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560472354-b33ff0c44a43?w=800\",\"description\":\"Vibrant community center promoting social engagement and recreational activities.\",\"location\":\"Sharjah, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"Recreational Facilities\",\"Social Spaces\",\"Event Venues\"]},{\"id\":\"10\",\"title\":\"High-Rise Business Plaza\",\"category\":\"Commercial\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?w=800\",\"description\":\"Multi-story business plaza offering flexible office spaces and collaborative environments.\",\"location\":\"Dubai, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"Flexible Offices\",\"Collaborative Hubs\",\"Retail Outlets\"]},{\"id\":\"11\",\"title\":\"Advanced Logistics Warehouse\",\"category\":\"Industrial\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581091226825-a6a2a5aee158?w=800\",\"description\":\"State-of-the-art warehouse facility optimized for efficient supply chain management.\",\"location\":\"Umm Al Quwain, UAE\",\"year\":\"2022\",\"features\":[\"Automated Storage\",\"Supply Chain Tech\",\"Scalable Design\"]},{\"id\":\"12\",\"title\":\"Heavy Industry Complex\",\"category\":\"Industrial\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=800\",\"description\":\"Robust industrial complex supporting heavy manufacturing and processing operations.\",\"location\":\"Ajman, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"Heavy Machinery\",\"Processing Units\",\"Safety Protocols\"]},{\"id\":\"13\",\"title\":\"Research Institute Headquarters\",\"category\":\"Institutional\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1434030216411-0b793f4b4173?w=800\",\"description\":\"Cutting-edge research institute fostering scientific advancement and collaboration.\",\"location\":\"Dubai, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"Research Labs\",\"Innovation Hubs\",\"Collaborative Spaces\"]},{\"id\":\"14\",\"title\":\"Public Library and Archive\",\"category\":\"Institutional\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523050854058-8df90110c9f1?w=800\",\"description\":\"Modern library serving as a knowledge hub with digital and physical resources.\",\"location\":\"Abu Dhabi, UAE\",\"year\":\"2022\",\"features\":[\"Digital Archives\",\"Reading Areas\",\"Educational Programs\"]},{\"id\":\"15\",\"title\":\"Neighborhood Cultural Hub\",\"category\":\"Community\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517457373958-b7bdd4587200?w=800\",\"description\":\"Cultural center offering arts, workshops, and community events for local residents.\",\"location\":\"Ras Al Khaimah, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"Arts Workshops\",\"Cultural Events\",\"Youth Programs\"]},{\"id\":\"16\",\"title\":\"Family Wellness Center\",\"category\":\"Community\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560472354-b33ff0c44a43?w=800\",\"description\":\"Wellness facility providing health services, fitness classes, and family support.\",\"location\":\"Fujairah, UAE\",\"year\":\"2022\",\"features\":[\"Fitness Classes\",\"Health Services\",\"Family Support\"]}],\"categories\":[\"All\",\"Urban\",\"Commercial\",\"Industrial\",\"Institutional\",\"Community\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"titleColor\":\"#000000\",\"subtitleColor\":\"#EF4130\"}},{\"id\":\"strategic-consulting-methodology\",\"type\":\"strategic-consulting-methodology\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Our Project Approach\",\"subtitle\":\"A Proven End-to-End Framework for Excellence\",\"description\":\"Our structured methodology blends strategy, design, technology, and execution. Every project is an opportunity to innovate, collaborate, and deliver lasting value.\",\"methodology\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Pre-Approval Strategy\",\"description\":\"Feasibility assessments, design compliance checks, and pre-approval consultations.\",\"icon\":\"🔍\",\"color\":\"#EF4130\",\"duration\":\"2–4 weeks\",\"deliverables\":[\"Site feasibility report\",\"Zoning compliance analysis\",\"Initial design concept\",\"Stakeholder consultation minutes\",\"Pre-application meeting notes\"],\"tools\":[\"Zoning regulation databases\",\"Site analysis software\",\"Compliance checklists\",\"Stakeholder mapping tools\",\"Feasibility assessment frameworks\"]},{\"id\":\"2\",\"title\":\"Documentation & Submission\",\"description\":\"Preparing and submitting architectural, MEP, and safety documentation.\",\"icon\":\"📘\",\"color\":\"#d63324\",\"duration\":\"4–8 weeks\",\"deliverables\":[\"Complete architectural drawings\",\"MEP engineering plans\",\"Fire safety documentation\",\"Structural calculations\",\"Environmental impact assessment\"],\"tools\":[\"CAD software\",\"BIM modeling tools\",\"Document management systems\",\"Compliance tracking software\",\"Digital submission portals\"]},{\"id\":\"3\",\"title\":\"Authority Coordination\",\"description\":\"Liaising with government authorities and other key agencies.\",\"icon\":\"⚙️\",\"color\":\"#b52a1f\",\"duration\":\"Project-dependent\",\"deliverables\":[\"Authority meeting minutes\",\"NOC applications\",\"Permit tracking reports\",\"Compliance certificates\",\"Agency coordination logs\"],\"tools\":[\"Government portal access\",\"Meeting scheduling systems\",\"Document tracking software\",\"Compliance databases\",\"Communication platforms\"]},{\"id\":\"4\",\"title\":\"Issue Resolution\",\"description\":\"Proactively addressing feedback, design modifications, and additional requirements.\",\"icon\":\"🚀\",\"color\":\"#EF4130\",\"duration\":\"8–16+ weeks\",\"deliverables\":[\"Design modification proposals\",\"Authority feedback responses\",\"Revised submission packages\",\"Compliance gap analysis\",\"Resolution status reports\"],\"tools\":[\"Issue tracking systems\",\"Design modification software\",\"Compliance gap analysis tools\",\"Revision management platforms\",\"Stakeholder communication logs\"]},{\"id\":\"5\",\"title\":\"Final Clearance\",\"description\":\"Securing final NOCs and compliance certificates\",\"icon\":\"📈\",\"color\":\"#d63324\",\"duration\":\"Ongoing\",\"deliverables\":[\"Final building permits\",\"Completion certificates\",\"All NOCs collection\",\"Occupancy certificates\",\"Project closure documentation\"],\"tools\":[\"Permit tracking systems\",\"Certificate management software\",\"Final inspection checklists\",\"Document archiving systems\",\"Compliance verification tools\"]}],\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"titleColor\":\"#000000\",\"subtitleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"showConnectors\":true,\"connectorColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"showDetails\":true,\"ctaButtonLink\":\"/contact\"}}]', '2025-11-26 13:24:34', 'raus@gmail.com', 0, NULL),
('1764143697875', '1763141252409', '[{\"id\":\"strategic-consulting-hero\",\"type\":\"strategic-consulting-hero\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Strategic Consulting & Advisory Solutions\",\"subtitle\":\"Strategic Advisory for High-Impact Growth\",\"description\":\"We offer expert guidance across real estate, infrastructure, urban planning, and digital transformation—helping clients turn vision into strategic, actionable plans that drive sustainable and measurable growth.\",\"primaryButtonText\":\"Get in Touch\",\"primaryButtonLink\":\"/contact\",\"secondaryButtonText\":\"Our Services\",\"secondaryButtonLink\":\"#strategic-consulting-services\",\"backgroundImage\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?w=1920\",\"backgroundVideo\":\"\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#fffff\",\"textColor\":\"white\",\"titleColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"subtitleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"primaryButtonColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"secondaryButtonColor\":\"#374151\",\"overlayOpacity\":0.5,\"showParticles\":true,\"showFloatingElements\":true,\"subtitleSize\":\"large\",\"showStats\":true}},{\"id\":\"strategic-consulting-hero-text-1\",\"type\":\"strategic-consulting-paragraph-hero\",\"content\":{\"paragraph1TextColor\":\"#000000\",\"paragraph1Text\":\"Strategic Consulting & Advisory Solutions empower clients to navigate complexity and seize opportunity across real estate, infrastructure, spatial planning, urban development and digital transformation. We combine market intelligence, technical depth, and policy awareness to craft holistic, future-ready strategies that turn challenges into growth engines.\",\"paragraph1BackgroundColor\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"paragraph1OverlayOpacity\":0.1,\"paragraph1TextSize\":\"text-5xl\",\"paragraph1TextAlign\":\"center\"}},{\"id\":\"strategic-consulting-hero-text-2\",\"type\":\"strategic-consulting-paragraph-feature\"},{\"id\":\"strategic-consulting-hero-text-3\",\"type\":\"strategic-consulting-paragraph-conclusion\",\"content\":{\"paragraph3Text\":\"RAUS is anchored in insight, foresight and impact. These principles guide every engagement—from strategy to execution—delivering tailored solutions, informed decisions and sustainable growth across every sector we serve.\",\"paragraph3BackgroundPattern\":\"lines\"}},{\"id\":\"infrastructure-advisory-content-1\",\"type\":\"infrastructure-advisory-content\",\"content\":{\"infraParagraph1\":\"Our Infrastructure Advisory services support clients in planning, designing, and delivering large-scale developments that are resilient, efficient, and future-ready. We bring together technical expertise, policy insight, and data-driven strategy to guide infrastructure decision-making from concept to completion.\",\"infraParagraph2\":\"We help organizations evaluate feasibility, optimize investment, reduce risk, and ensure that infrastructure assets deliver lasting value for the communities they serve. With a focus on sustainability, compliance, and long-term performance, our advisory approach aligns vision, operational needs, and real-world conditions to create infrastructure that stands the test of time.\",\"infraAccentColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"infraImagePosition\":\"left\",\"infraImageHeight\":100}}]', '2025-11-26 13:24:58', 'selva@imaginetventures.com', 0, NULL),
