 aligns with the United Nations Sustainable Development Goals, ensuring that our projects contribute to global sustainability targets. Our work advances better health and well-being (SDG 3), clean energy (SDG 7), economic growth (SDG 8), sustainable cities (SDG 11), responsible consumption (SDG 12), climate action (SDG 13), life on land (SDG 15) and strong partnerships (SDG 17). Through this alignment, we ensure that every project is part of a broader mission to create resilient, inclusive and future-ready environments.\"},{\"id\":\"environment-sustainability-responsibility-1\",\"type\":\"environment-sustainability-responsibility\",\"description\":\"Environmental responsibility at RAUS is embedded into every phase—planning, design, construction and operations. Our focus is on developing high-performance, low-impact spaces that balance human needs with ecological preservation.\",\"supportingText\":\"Through innovation, regulatory compliance and strategic foresight, we deliver sustainable solutions engineered to endure and evolve.\",\"principles\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Future-Focused Design\",\"description\":\"Solutions crafted to excel today while adapting to tomorrow’s challenges.\",\"accent\":\"#38bdf8\"},{\"id\":\"2\",\"title\":\"Integrated Responsibility\",\"description\":\"Environmental, social and economic priorities aligned across the entire lifecycle.\",\"accent\":\"#34d399\"},{\"id\":\"3\",\"title\":\"Low Impact, High Value\",\"description\":\"Smart materials, energy-efficient systems and circular practices that reduce footprint without compromising performance.\",\"accent\":\"#fbbf24\"}]},{\"id\":\"environment-sustainability-services-1\",\"type\":\"environment-sustainability-services\",\"description\":\"A broad suite of environmental and sustainable development services support our clients in achieving regulatory alignment, operational efficiency and long-term ecological value.\",\"domains\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Environment Advisory\",\"description\":\"Strategy-first guidance that balances policy alignment with ecological outcomes.\"},{\"id\":\"2\",\"title\":\"HSE Reporting\",\"description\":\"Data-driven health, safety and environment reporting for total compliance clarity.\"},{\"id\":\"3\",\"title\":\"Waste Management\",\"description\":\"Circular waste practices that reduce impact and unlock resource recovery.\"},{\"id\":\"4\",\"title\":\"Sustainable Development\",\"description\":\"Integrated planning that embeds sustainability metrics into every phase.\"},{\"id\":\"5\",\"title\":\"ESG Advisory\",\"description\":\"Frameworks that connect governance rigor with measurable sustainability goals.\"},{\"id\":\"6\",\"title\":\"Carbon Advisory\",\"description\":\"Carbon accounting, reduction roadmaps and transition strategies.\"}],\"accentColor\":\"#EF4130\"},{\"id\":\"environment-sustainability-mindset-1\",\"type\":\"environment-sustainability-mindset\",\"accentColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"intro\":\"Sustainability is our pledge to build responsibly, act consciously and leave a positive legacy. It influences how we plan, design and deliver—ensuring every project supports environmental health, community well-being and long-term resilience.\",\"supporting\":\"Sustainability is more than compliance; it is a mindset. Our environmental services are driven by a commitment to future resilience, low-impact development and long-term ecological value.\",\"extended\":\"Every initiative integrates sustainability from the ground up, aligned with global standards, local regulations and the needs of the communities we serve.\",\"highlights\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Future Resilience\",\"description\":\"Adaptive strategies that anticipate climate realities and protect investments.\"},{\"id\":\"2\",\"title\":\"Low-Impact Development\",\"description\":\"Design and delivery methodologies that minimize disruption and conserve resources.\"},{\"id\":\"3\",\"title\":\"Ecological Value\",\"description\":\"Outcomes that enhance biodiversity, healthy communities and regenerative growth.\"}]},{\"id\":\"environment-sustainability-strategy-1\",\"type\":\"environment-sustainability-strategy\",\"accentColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"description\":\"Our strategic environmental solutions help clients achieve compliance, reduce risk and future-proof their infrastructure. We combine scientific analysis, regulatory understanding and industry best practices to deliver meaningful outcomes.\",\"focusAreas\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Environmental Planning & Compliance\",\"description\":\"Strategies to satisfy regulatory frameworks while enhancing ecological outcomes and minimizing risk.\"},{\"id\":\"2\",\"title\":\"Carbon & Climate Risk Assessment\",\"description\":\"Measuring emissions, evaluating climate impacts and defining mitigation strategies to future-proof assets.\"},{\"id\":\"3\",\"title\":\"ESG & Climate Strategy\",\"description\":\"Developing Environment, Social and Governance frameworks aligned with climate resilience and long-term value.\"},{\"id\":\"4\",\"title\":\"Sustainability Advisory\",\"description\":\"Integrating low-carbon materials, energy-efficient systems and green certifications across each project lifecycle.\"},{\"id\":\"5\",\"title\":\"Green Building & Urban Design\",\"description\":\"High-performance design solutions that reduce energy demand, enhance air quality and improve occupant well-being.\"}]},{\"id\":\"environment-sustainability-commitment\",\"type\":\"environment-sustainability-commitment\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Our Commitment\",\"description1\":\"Sustainability is our pledge to build responsibly, act consciously, and leave a positive legacy. By integrating environmental intelligence with innovative technologies and human-centered design, RAUS delivers solutions that support climate resilience, ecological balance, and long-term community prosperity.\",\"description2\":\"We believe that shaping tomorrow begins with the actions we take today—and we remain committed to creating places where people thrive, ecosystems flourish, and future generations are protected.\",\"commitments\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"quote\":\"Building responsibly means creating spaces that not only serve today\'s needs but protect tomorrow\'s possibilities.\",\"author\":\"RAUS Leadership\",\"role\":\"Environmental Stewardship\",\"icon\":\"🌱\",\"color\":\"#10b981\"},{\"id\":\"2\",\"quote\":\"Every project is an opportunity to advance sustainability and create lasting positive impact on our communities.\",\"author\":\"RAUS Team\",\"role\":\"Sustainable Development\",\"icon\":\"♻️\",\"color\":\"#3b82f6\"},{\"id\":\"3\",\"quote\":\"Innovation and environmental responsibility go hand in hand in shaping the future of our built environment.\",\"author\":\"RAUS Vision\",\"role\":\"Climate Action\",\"icon\":\"🌍\",\"color\":\"#f59e0b\"}],\"backgroundColor\":\"#f8fafc\",\"textColor\":\"#1f2937\",\"titleColor\":\"#1f2937\",\"accentColor\":\"#059669\",\"quoteColor\":\"#374151\"},\"description1\":\"Sustainability is our pledge to build responsibly, act consciously and leave a positive legacy. By integrating environmental intelligence with innovative technologies and human-centered design, RAUS delivers solutions that support climate resilience, ecological balance and long-term community prosperity.\",\"description2\":\"We believe that shaping tomorrow begins with the actions we take today—and we remain committed to creating places where people thrive, ecosystems flourish and future generations are protected.\"}]', '2025-11-26 16:25:30', 'selva@imaginetventures.com', 0, NULL),
('1764154627897', '1763141252163', '[{\"id\":\"hero-3-1\",\"type\":\"at-a-glance-hero\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"At a Glance\",\"subtitle\":\"\",\"text\":\"\",\"description\":\"A snapshot of our journey, expertise and  impact\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?w=1600\",\"fontSize\":\"4rem\",\"color\":\"red\",\"backgroundImage\":\"https://jalgzgoha9oynfjc.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/image/1763148114007-925825.jpg\",\"backgroundVideo\":\"\",\"alignment\":\"center\",\"titleColor\":\"white\"},\"order\":0},{\"id\":\"who-we-are-3-2-1\",\"type\":\"who-we-are\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Who We Are\",\"text\":\"RAUS Integrated Project Management Services LLC is a dynamic, multi-disciplinary solutions partner founded in 2021 and headquartered in the UAE, with a fast-growing footprint in Tanzania, Nigeria and the broader Middle East. We’re not your typical consultancy. RAUS is purpose-built to redefine how future-ready environments are imagined, developed and optimized. From state-of-the-art infrastructure and digital ecosystems to sustainable architecture, ergonomic design and comprehensive fit-out services, we connect ambition with precision. By integrating diverse technical expertise under one roof, we ensure a seamless, single-source solution that respects deadlines, enhances quality and drives innovation at every stage.\",\"fontSize\":\"1.125rem\",\"color\":\"#414042\",\"sectionAlignment\":\"right\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://7exy4hnlmwjqhh3r.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/AtGlanceIntegratedProject-min.jpg\",\"titleColor\":\"#000\",\"textColor\":\"#3f3f3f\"},\"order\":1},{\"id\":\"dual-header-img-3-3\",\"type\":\"dual-header-img\",\"content\":{\"smallHeader\":\"Community & Society\",\"bigHeader\":\"Shaping the Future, \\nOne Community at a Time\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://7exy4hnlmwjqhh3r.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/AtGlanceShapingFuture-min.jpg\",\"description\":\"\",\"showButton\":false,\"showScrollIndicator\":false,\"overlayOpacity\":0.4,\"smallHeaderColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"bigHeaderFontSize\":\"\"},\"order\":2},{\"id\":\"home-services-3-4\",\"type\":\"at-a-glance-service\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Shaping Better Cities\",\"subtitle\":\"Integrating Responsibility, Inclusivity and Collaboration in Every Project\",\"services\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"iconType\":\"lucide\",\"iconName\":\"Home\",\"title\":\"Corporate Social Responsibility\",\"description\":\"Our corporate projects reflect a deep\\ncommitment to society. We embed ethical\\npractices, inclusivity and sustainability into\\nevery phase—aligning business success with\\ncommunity progress and social betterment.\\n\"},{\"id\":\"2\",\"iconType\":\"lucide\",\"iconName\":\"Globe\",\"title\":\"Public Spaces with Purpose\",\"description\":\"We create parks, plazas and cultural hubs that\\nunite people and celebrate communities. Our\\nhuman-focused design transforms spaces into\\nplaces that foster connections, support\\ninteraction and enhance quality of life.\"},{\"id\":\"3\",\"iconType\":\"lucide\",\"iconName\":\"Users\",\"title\":\"Designing for Diversity & Inclusivity\",\"description\":\"We champion designs that are accessible,\\ninclusive and culturally resonant. Our solutions\\ncelebrate diversity, crafting spaces where\\nevery identity feels welcome and where\\ncommunities can thrive together in harmony.\"},{\"id\":\"4\",\"iconType\":\"lucide\",\"iconName\":\"Truck\",\"title\":\"Community Integration & Partnerships\",\"description\":\"We believe in collaboration and meaningful\\npartnerships. By engaging local stakeholders,\\ncivic groups and NGOs, we align every project\\nwith community needs, ensuring a strong\\nsocial fabric and lasting positive impact.\"}],\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"titleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"subtitleColor\":\"#333333\",\"serviceBackgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"iconColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"alignment\":\"center\",\"textColor\":\"black\"},\"order\":3},{\"id\":\"strategic-consulting-expertise\",\"type\":\"strategic-consulting-expertise\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Core Expertise\",\"subtitle\":\"Building High-Performance, Future-Ready Systems\",\"description\":\"Our multidisciplinary expertise spans infrastructure, environmental systems, digital ecosystems, real estate and mobility—allowing us to deliver tailored, high-value solutions across complex industries.\",\"expertiseAreas\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Real Estate & Construction\",\"description\":\"Integrated architecture, engineering, design & build execution for high-quality, future-ready environments.\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"icon\":\"🏗️\",\"color\":\"#EF4130\",\"skills\":[\"Integrated design & build\",\"Digital twin simulations\",\"BIM-enabled precision\",\"Sustainable architecture\"],\"achievements\":[\"Delivered multi-sector real estate projects\",\"Advanced immersive design adoption\"]},{\"id\":\"2\",\"title\":\"Digital Transformation\",\"description\":\"Smart, connected spaces leveraging BIM, IoT, automation and AI analytics.\",\"year\":\"2022\",\"icon\":\"🔌\",\"color\":\"#d63324\",\"skills\":[\"Smart building systems\",\"Data-driven decision intelligence\",\"Cloud collaboration\",\"AI-enhanced operations\"],\"achievements\":[\"Implemented smart ecosystems across sectors\",\"BIM-integrated workflows\"]},{\"id\":\"3\",\"title\":\"Environment & Sustainability\",\"description\":\"Low-impact, high-value sustainability solutions aligned with SDGs and global standards.\",\"year\":\"2021\",\"icon\":\"🌍\",\"color\":\"#b52a1f\",\"skills\":[\"Environmental planning\",\"Carbon advisory\",\"ESG frameworks\",\"Green building strategies\"],\"achievements\":[\"Circular material strategies deployed\",\"Reduced carbon strategies for major projects\"]},{\"id\":\"4\",\"title\":\"Mobility & Transport\",\"description\":\"Connected, intelligent mobility solutions backed by digital systems and sustainable design.\",\"year\":\"2020\",\"icon\":\"🚈\",\"color\":\"#EF4130\",\"skills\":[\"Urban mobility planning\",\"Smart transport systems\",\"Real-time mobility intelligence\",\"Future-ready multimodal design\"],\"achievements\":[\"Developed integrated mobility models\",\"Optimized multimodal transport flows\"]},{\"id\":\"5\",\"title\":\"Strategic Advisory\",\"description\":\"Multi-sector guidance across infrastructure, digital ecosystems and urban development.\",\"year\":\"2019\",\"icon\":\"📊\",\"color\":\"#d63324\",\"skills\":[\"Strategic frameworks\",\"Policy alignment\",\"Urban planning\",\"Sustainable economic strategies\"],\"achievements\":[\"Led advisory for national-scale programs\",\"Supported major city-scale masterplans\"]}],\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"titleColor\":\"#000000\",\"subtitleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"timelineColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"showAchievements\":true},\"order\":4},{\"id\":\"text-3-5\",\"type\":\"text\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Every space we create is a promise—a commitment to the people who live, work and play there. Together, we’re not just shaping structures; we’re shaping futures.\",\"text\":\"\",\"fontSize\":\"1.5rem\",\"color\":\"#db0000\",\"alignment\":\"center\"},\"order\":6},{\"id\":\"value-card-3-6\",\"type\":\"philosophy-with-hover-cards\",\"content\":{\"0\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"value\":\"90%\",\"valueColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"description\":\"Project Success Rate\"},\"items\":[{\"value\":\"78%\",\"valueColor\":\"#ff2d1a\",\"description\":\"of customers prefer brands that prioritize social responsibility\"},{\"value\":\"25%\",\"valueColor\":\"#0074cc\",\"description\":\"Increase in social interaction in communities with quality public spaces.\"},{\"value\":\"20%\",\"valueColor\":\"#37008a\",\"description\":\"reduction in project delays through local partnerships\"},{\"value\":\"60%\",\"valueColor\":\"#132a86\",\"description\":\" of employees feel more engaged in companies with strong CSR values.\"}],\"columns\":{\"base\":1,\"sm\":1,\"md\":2,\"lg\":4,\"xl\":5},\"backgroundColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"fontSize\":\"sm\",\"accentColor\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"showPhilosophy\":\"true\",\"text\":\"We believe that the true measure of progress is how it uplifts the people and communities it touches. From bustling corporate campuses to vibrant public spaces, our work is guided by a simple yet powerful principle: build places where people feel a sense of belonging, inspiration and pride\"},\"order\":7},{\"id\":\"services-at-a-glance-1\",\"type\":\"at-a-glance-extra-service\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Sustainable Commitment\",\"subtitle\":\"Building a Sustainable Legacy, Today and Beyond\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"titleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"subtitleColor\":\"#ec4899\",\"iconColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"cardBackgroundColor\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"textColor\":\"#2e2e2e\",\"alignment\":\"center\",\"services\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"iconType\":\"lucide\",\"iconName\":\"Target\",\"title\":\"Designing for a Sustainable Future\",\"description\":\"We integrate sustainable thinking from the earliest stages of every project. Our designs prioritize energy efficiency, reduced carbon footprint and adaptable solutions that stand the test of time ensuring spaces that grow with their communities.\"},{\"id\":\"2\",\"iconType\":\"lucide\",\"iconName\":\"Zap\",\"title\":\"Smart Resource Management\",\"description\":\"Every project reflects our dedication to responsible resource use. From eco-friendly materials to water conservation and waste reduction, we embed sustainability into every detail, ensuring projects that respect both budget and the environment.\",\"iconUrl\":\"\"},{\"id\":\"3\",\"iconType\":\"lucide\",\"iconName\":\"Shield\",\"title\":\"Innovation-Driven Solutions\",\"description\":\"We harness the power of technology — from digital twins to AI-powered analytics — to optimize design, construction and operations. This innovation ensures our projects are not just sustainable but future-ready.\"},{\"id\":\"4\",\"iconType\":\"lucide\",\"iconName\":\"TrendingUp\",\"title\":\"Community-Centric Sustainability\",\"description\":\"We believe that sustainability is about people. Our commitment extends beyond technical solutions to include social responsibility, local partnerships and inclusive community development that empowers every voice.\"}]}},{\"id\":\"value-card-6-6\",\"type\":\"philosophy-with-hover-cards\",\"content\":{\"items\":[{\"value\":\"78%\",\"valueColor\":\"#ff2d1a\",\"description\":\"of customers prefer brands that prioritize social responsibility\"},{\"value\":\"25%\",\"valueColor\":\"#0074cc\",\"description\":\"Increase in social interaction in communities with quality public spaces.\"},{\"value\":\"20%\",\"valueColor\":\"#37008a\",\"description\":\"reduction in project delays through local partnerships\"},{\"value\":\"60%\",\"valueColor\":\"#132a86\",\"description\":\" of employees feel more engaged in companies with strong CSR values.\"}],\"columns\":{\"base\":1,\"sm\":1,\"md\":2,\"lg\":4,\"xl\":5},\"backgroundColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"fontSize\":\"sm\",\"accentColor\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"layoutDirection\":\"right-philosophy\",\"text\":\"At the heart of everything we do lies a deep-rooted commitment to sustainability , a commitment that drives our purpose, shapes our decisions and defines our legacy. From innovative design strategies that minimize environmental impact to responsible resource management that ensures every material and process is optimized, our approach goes beyond compliance. We set new standards for sustainability, creating spaces and systems that deliver lasting value for people, communities and the planet alike\",\"cards\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"value\":\"72%\",\"description\":\"of clients prefer sustainable solutions over traditional ones when choosing project partners.\",\"valueColor\":\"#ef4130\"},{\"id\":\"2\",\"value\":\"25%\",\"description\":\"of corporate clients prioritize eco-conscious partners.\",\"valueColor\":\"#ef4130\"},{\"id\":\"3\",\"value\":\"80%\",\"description\":\"of stakeholders see sustainability as vital for community well-being.\",\"valueColor\":\"#ef4130\"},{\"id\":\"4\",\"value\":\"68%\",\"description\":\"of sustainable buildings cut costs by 30%.\",\"valueColor\":\"#ef4130\"}]},\"order\":8}]', '2025-11-26 16:27:08', 'selva@imaginetventures.com', 0, NULL),
('1764154864477', '1763141252219', '[{\"id\":\"our-values-hero-1\",\"type\":\"our-value-hero-banner\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Our Values\",\"subtitle\":\"Building Excellence Through Integrity\",\"description\":\"We are committed to delivering exceptional quality, fostering innovation and maintaining the highest standards of integrity in everything we do. Our values guide every decision we make and every project we undertake.\",\"buttonText\":\"Explore Our Values\",\"buttonLink\":\"/contact\",\"buttonVariant\":\"primary\",\"buttonIcon\":\"arrow-right\",\"buttonAnimation\":\"slide\",\"secondaryButtonText\":\"Learn More\",\"secondaryButtonLink\":\"/contact\",\"secondaryButtonVariant\":\"outline\",\"secondaryButtonIcon\":\"external-link\",\"backgroundImage\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?q=80&w=2070\",\"backgroundVideo\":\"\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#1f2937\",\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"titleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"subtitleColor\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"alignment\":\"center\",\"overlay\":true,\"overlayOpacity\":0.6,\"overlayColor\":\"#000000\",\"titleSize\":\"6xl\",\"subtitleSize\":\"6xl\",\"descriptionSize\":\"xl\",\"animationEnabled\":true,\"animationStyle\":\"fade\",\"showScrollIndicator\":true,\"height\":\"full\"}},{\"id\":\"our-core-values-1\",\"type\":\"our-core-values\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Our Core Values\",\"subtitle\":\"At RAUS, our values define who we are, guide every decision we make and inspire the impact we aim to create. We believe in building more than projects — we build trust, responsibility and a legacy of sustainable progress.\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"titleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"subtitleColor\":\"#333333\",\"cardBackgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"cardTextColor\":\"#333333\",\"cardTitleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"accentColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"animationEnabled\":true,\"cardStyle\":\"elevated\",\"layout\":\"grid\",\"values\":[{\"number\":1,\"title\":\"Integrity in Every Action\",\"description\":\"We operate with transparency, honesty and accountability — ensuring that every partnership, process and project reflects the highest ethical standards. Integrity isn\'t just a principle at RAUS; it\'s our foundation for lasting relationships.\",\"icon\":\"shield\"},{\"number\":2,\"title\":\"Innovation with Purpose\",\"description\":\"We embrace emerging technologies, data intelligence and creative thinking not for novelty, but for meaningful progress. Every innovation we adopt drives efficiency, enhances performance and creates value that endures.\",\"icon\":\"lightbulb\"},{\"number\":3,\"title\":\"Sustainability as a Standard\",\"description\":\"Sustainability is embedded in everything we do — from design and material selection to operations and governance. We go beyond compliance to champion circular economy practices, low-carbon solutions and community well-being.\",\"icon\":\"leaf\"},{\"number\":4,\"title\":\"Collaboration for Collective Success\",\"description\":\"We believe the best outcomes come from shared vision and teamwork. Our multidisciplinary approach unites experts, partners and communities to deliver integrated, future-ready solutions that serve people and the planet.\",\"icon\":\"users\"},{\"number\":5,\"title\":\"Excellence through Accountability\",\"description\":\"We strive for excellence in every deliverable, guided by data, precision and responsibility. Each milestone is measured not just by results, but by the value it adds to our clients, our communities, and the environment.\",\"icon\":\"target\"}]}},{\"id\":\"corporate-governance-1\",\"type\":\"corporate-governance\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Corporate Governance\",\"subtitle\":\"Building Trust Through Transparency\",\"description\":\"Corporate governance at RAUS is not a compliance checklist — it\'s our promise of integrity, responsibility and accountability. It ensures that we innovate boldly, partner responsibly and deliver long-term value for all stakeholders.\",\"frameworkTitle\":\"Governance Framework\",\"backgroundI