 engineering and construction management into a seamless process, ensuring projects move from vision to reality efficiently.\",\"Our approach leverages digital tools like BIM and computational fluid dynamics to enhance precision, optimize resources and accelerate timelines.\",\"Integrated approvals processes streamline delivery, reducing bottlenecks and ensuring every milestone aligns with client goals.\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"titleColor\":\"#000000\",\"subtitleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"backgroundImage\":\"https://jalgzgoha9oynfjc.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/image/1764140530478-908831.jpg\"},\"order\":2},{\"id\":\"real-estate-innovation-1\",\"type\":\"real-estate-innovation\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Design & Build Solution\",\"subtitle\":\"Industry\",\"sections\":[{\"id\":\"immersive-visualization\",\"title\":\"Immersive Visualization\",\"bulletPoints\":[\"Life-scale mixed-reality walkthroughs\",\"Real-time stakeholder collaboration\",\"Early-stage design refinements\"]},{\"id\":\"digital-twin-analytics\",\"title\":\"Digital Twin Analytics\",\"bulletPoints\":[\"Live-data monitoring of cost, schedule, quality\",\"Predictive \'what-if\' simulations\",\"Automated anomaly alerts\"]},{\"id\":\"sustainable-tech-integration\",\"title\":\"Sustainable Tech Integration\",\"bulletPoints\":[\"Low-carbon materials modeling\",\"AI-optimized resource allocation\",\"Net-zero performance tracking\"]}],\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"textColor\":\"#e6e6e6\",\"titleColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"subtitleColor\":\"#ff4433\",\"backgroundImage\":\"https://jalgzgoha9oynfjc.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/image/1764145012283-281537.jpg\",\"overlayOpacity\":0.61},\"order\":3},{\"id\":\"real-estate-design-build-1\",\"type\":\"real-estate-design-build\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Design & Build\",\"subtitle\":\"Unified Delivery\",\"description\":\"At RAUS, our Design & Build approach unifies vision, planning and execution under one roof—streamlining the journey from concept to reality. We integrate architectural creativity with construction precision to deliver spaces that are functional, future-ready and aligned with client goals.\",\"additionalText\":\"By managing both design and construction within a single contract, we minimize delays, reduce risks and ensure accountability at every stage. Our collaborative model enables faster decision-making, optimized costs and seamless coordination—resulting in high-quality outcomes that reflect both innovation and integrity.\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"titleColor\":\"#000000\",\"subtitleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"overlay\":false,\"backgroundImage\":\"https://jalgzgoha9oynfjc.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/image/1764161671120-449852.jpg\"},\"order\":4},{\"id\":\"virtual-reality-core-1\",\"type\":\"real-estate-virtual-reality\",\"content\":{\"eyebrow\":\"Virtual Reality\",\"title\":\"Immersive Delivery Systems\",\"description\":\"Virtual Reality (VR) takes our design process even further, offering an interactive experience that allows clients to explore every angle, adjust layouts, and refine finishes in real time. This hands-on approach not only enhances collaboration but also empowers clients to make informed decisions with confidence.\",\"supportingText\":\"By integrating these advanced tools into our workflow, we bridge the gap between imagination and reality—delivering spaces that truly resonate.\",\"statLabel\":\"raus.ae\",\"statValue\":\"16\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#030712\",\"cardBackground\":\"#000000\",\"gridColor\":\"#1f273a\",\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"titleColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"accentColor\":\"#dc2626\",\"features\":[{\"id\":\"immersive-visualization\",\"title\":\"Immersive Visualization\",\"bullets\":[\"Life-scale mixed-reality walkthroughs\",\"Real-time stakeholder collaboration\",\"Early-stage design refinements\"]},{\"id\":\"digital-twin-analytics\",\"title\":\"Digital Twin Analytics\",\"bullets\":[\"Live-data monitoring of cost, schedule, quality\",\"Predictive \\\"what-if\\\" simulations\",\"Automated anomaly alerts\"]},{\"id\":\"sustainable-tech\",\"title\":\"Sustainable Tech Integration\",\"bullets\":[\"Low-carbon materials modeling\",\"AI-optimized resource allocation\",\"Net-zero performance tracking\"]}],\"insights\":[{\"id\":\"immersive-solution\",\"title\":\"Immersive Solution\",\"description\":\"Virtual reality, augmented reality, and interactive 3D models allow stakeholders to fully engage with designs before construction begins—enabling faster alignment and more informed choices.\"},{\"id\":\"real-time-experience\",\"title\":\"Real-Time Experience\",\"description\":\"Live collaboration tools and instant visual feedback streamline the design-to-build process, ensuring agility and seamless coordination across teams.\"},{\"id\":\"data-driven\",\"title\":\"Data Driven Decisions\",\"description\":\"Design choices are guided by performance metrics, sustainability data, and user behavior insights—ensuring outcomes that are efficient and future ready.\"}],\"backgroundImage\":\"https://jalgzgoha9oynfjc.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/image/1764163712949-920019.jpg\",\"cardOverlayOpacity\":0.6,\"backgroundOverlayOpacity\":0.55,\"cardOverlay\":true}},{\"id\":\"real-estate-portfolio-1\",\"type\":\"real-estate-portfolio\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Industries\",\"subtitle\":\"Our Design and Build approach is grounded in creativity, collaboration and precision. ensuring architectural excellence, seamless delivery, & spaces that embody both form & function for lasting impact.\",\"description\":\"Explore our diverse portfolio of completed projects that demonstrate our commitment to quality, innovation and sustainable development.\",\"projects\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Luxury Residential Complex\",\"category\":\"Urban\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600607687939-ce8a6c25118c?w=800\",\"description\":\"A premium residential development featuring modern architecture and sustainable design.\",\"location\":\"Dubai, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"Sustainable Design\",\"Smart Home Technology\",\"Premium Amenities\"]},{\"id\":\"2\",\"title\":\"Commercial Tower\",\"category\":\"Commercial\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?w=800\",\"description\":\"State-of-the-art commercial tower with LEED certification and innovative workspace design.\",\"location\":\"Abu Dhabi, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"LEED Certified\",\"Modern Workspaces\",\"Energy Efficient\"]},{\"id\":\"3\",\"title\":\"Mixed-Use Development\",\"category\":\"Urban\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600596542815-ffad4c1539a9?w=800\",\"description\":\"Integrated mixed-use development combining retail, office and residential spaces.\",\"location\":\"Sharjah, UAE\",\"year\":\"2022\",\"features\":[\"Mixed-Use\",\"Community Focus\",\"Retail Integration\"]},{\"id\":\"4\",\"title\":\"Sustainable Office Complex\",\"category\":\"Commercial\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497366216548-37526070297c?w=800\",\"description\":\"Eco-friendly office complex with green building certifications and modern amenities.\",\"location\":\"Dubai, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"Green Building\",\"Modern Amenities\",\"Energy Efficient\"]},{\"id\":\"5\",\"title\":\"Luxury Villa Community\",\"category\":\"Urban\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600596542815-ffad4c1539a9?w=800\",\"description\":\"Exclusive villa community with premium finishes and resort-style amenities.\",\"location\":\"Ras Al Khaimah, UAE\",\"year\":\"2022\",\"features\":[\"Premium Finishes\",\"Resort Amenities\",\"Private Security\"]},{\"id\":\"6\",\"title\":\"Urban Retail Center\",\"category\":\"Urban\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1449824913935-59a10b8d2000?w=800\",\"description\":\"Modern retail and entertainment center serving the urban community.\",\"location\":\"Fujairah, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"Retail Spaces\",\"Entertainment\",\"Urban Design\"]},{\"id\":\"7\",\"title\":\"Industrial Manufacturing Park\",\"category\":\"Industrial\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=800\",\"description\":\"Advanced industrial park with state-of-the-art manufacturing facilities and logistics support.\",\"location\":\"Ajman, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"Manufacturing Facilities\",\"Logistics Hub\",\"Sustainable Operations\"]},{\"id\":\"8\",\"title\":\"Modern University Campus\",\"category\":\"Institutional\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523050854058-8df90110c9f1?w=800\",\"description\":\"Contemporary university campus designed for innovation and academic excellence.\",\"location\":\"Abu Dhabi, UAE\",\"year\":\"2022\",\"features\":[\"Academic Facilities\",\"Research Labs\",\"Green Spaces\"]},{\"id\":\"9\",\"title\":\"Community Recreation Center\",\"category\":\"Community\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560472354-b33ff0c44a43?w=800\",\"description\":\"Vibrant community center promoting social engagement and recreational activities.\",\"location\":\"Sharjah, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"Recreational Facilities\",\"Social Spaces\",\"Event Venues\"]},{\"id\":\"10\",\"title\":\"High-Rise Business Plaza\",\"category\":\"Commercial\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?w=800\",\"description\":\"Multi-story business plaza offering flexible office spaces and collaborative environments.\",\"location\":\"Dubai, UAE\",\"year\":\"2023\",\"features\":[\"Flexible Offices\",\"Collaborative Hubs\",\"Retail Outlets\"]},{\"id\":\"11\",\"title\":\"Advanced Logistics Warehouse\",\"category\":\"Industrial\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581091226825-a6a2a5aee158?w=800\",\"description\":\"State-of-the-art warehouse facility optimized for efficient supply chain management.\",\"location\":\"Umm Al Quwain, UAE\",\"year\":\"2022\",\"features\":[\"Automated Storage\",\"Sup