ility.\"},{\"title\":\"Risk, Quality & Timeline Assurance\",\"description\":\"Implements rigorous controls to mitigate risks, uphold standards, and ensure timely, on-budget project completion.\"}],\"image\":\"https://jalgzgoha9oynfjc.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/image/1764244871917-25592.jpg\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"textColor\":\"#0f172a\",\"accentColor\":\"#EF4130\"}},{\"id\":\"real-estate-project-approach-1\",\"type\":\"real-estate-project-approach\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Our Project Approach:\",\"subtitle\":\"Building Beyond Boundaries\",\"description\":\"At RAUS, our project approach is more than a process—it\'s a mindset and a promise. We blend strategic insight, technical precision, and innovative thinking to transform ideas into high-performing, future-ready realities. Our approach is designed to unlock hidden potential, streamline complexities, and empower every stakeholder to succeed.\\n\\nBy embracing cutting-edge technologies, data-driven decision-making, and sustainable practices, we future-proof every project and prepare it to thrive in an ever-changing world. Our commitment goes beyond mere delivery—we build with purpose, accountability, and a vision for tomorrow and enduring success for our clients.\",\"closingText\":\"Every project is an opportunity to innovate, collaborate, and deliver lasting value. At RAUS, we don\'t just build projects—we build partnerships that stand the test of time.\",\"flowDiagramImage\":\"\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"titleColor\":\"#000000\",\"subtitleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"accentColor\":\"#EF4130\"},\"order\":6}]', '2025-11-27 17:31:19', 'raus@gmail.com', 0, NULL),
('1764244949383', '13433141252653', '[{\"id\":\"mobility-hero-1\",\"type\":\"mobility-hero\",\"content\":{\"textColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"heroShowScrollIndicator\":true,\"heroPrimaryActionLink\":\"/contact\",\"accentColor\":\"#000000\",\"heroSecondaryAccentColor\":\"#EF4130\"}},{\"id\":\"mobility-features-1\",\"type\":\"mobility-features\",\"content\":{\"accentColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#404040\",\"textColor\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"featuresDescription\":\"Layering transit, critical infrastructure, and data services into unified delivery models that streamline mobility, enhance operational efficiency, and enable seamless coordination across urban networks. By integrating transport systems, utility frameworks, and digital intelligence into a single strategic platform, we create connected environments that are scalable, resilient and ready for the future.\"}},{\"id\":\"infrastructure-advisory-content-1\",\"type\":\"infrastructure-advisory-content\",\"content\":{\"infraTitle\":\"Full-Spectrum Delivery\",\"infraParagraph1\":\"From concept design to full-scale deployment, we provide end-to-end delivery solutions for power plants, utility networks, industrial facilities, and national infrastructure programs.\",\"infraParagraph2\":\"Our integrated model ensures seamless coordination across engineering, procurement, construction, and commissioning—reducing delays, increasing efficiency, and guaranteeing consistent quality.\",\"infraBackgroundColor\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"infraTitleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"infraTextColor\":\"#000000\",\"overlayOpacity\":0.05,\"backgroundStyle\":\"gradient-mesh\",\"borderRadiusStyle\":\"curved-edges\",\"infraImage\":\"https://jalgzgoha9oynfjc.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/image/1764244656459-993932.jpg\"}},{\"id\":\"infrastructure-advisory-content-2\",\"type\":\"infrastructure-advisory-content\",\"content\":{\"infraTitle\":\"Clean Energy, Built-In\",\"infraParagraph1\":\"Smart modernization solutions and low-carbon transition strategies that help organizations meet sustainability mandates and ESG performance targets.\",\"infraParagraph2\":\"We integrate renewable technologies—solar, wind, hybrid systems—and implement energy-efficient upgrades that reduce emissions while maintaining operational reliability.\",\"infraImagePosition\":\"left\",\"infraBackgroundColor\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"infraTitleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"infraTextColor\":\"#000000\",\"infraImage\":\"https://jalgzgoha9oynfjc.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/image/1764244711778-357572.jpg\",\"backgroundStyle\":\"organic-waves\"}},{\"id\":\"infrastructure-advisory-content-3\",\"type\":\"infrastructure-advisory-content\",\"content\":{\"infraTitle\":\"Future-Ready Systems\",\"infraParagraph1\":\"Resilient, data-driven infrastructure designed to adapt, scale, and perform under evolving economic, environmental, and technological conditions.\",\"infraParagraph2\":\"From digital monitoring to predictive maintenance and scalable system architecture, we help build infrastructure that stays reliable, efficient, and responsive for decades.\",\"infraBackgroundColor\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"infraTitleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"infraTextColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundStyle\":\"gradient-mesh\",\"infraImage\":\"https://jalgzgoha9oynfjc.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/image/1764244767539-428450.jpg\"}},{\"id\":\"mobility-conclusion-1\",\"type\":\"mobility-conclusion\",\"content\":{\"textColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"accentColor\":\"#3B82F6\"}}]', '2025-11-27 17:32:29', 'selva@imaginetventures.com', 0, NULL),
