ng user experience for all.\",\"infraParagraph2\":\"Through cohesive planning, we create mobility networks where public transit, active mobility, shared transport and digital services operate as a single, interconnected system supporting seamless journeys.\",\"infraBackgroundColor\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"infraTitleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"infraTextColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundStyle\":\"gradient-mesh\",\"infraImage\":\"https://jalgzgoha9oynfjc.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/image/1764246659199-753806.jpg\"}},{\"id\":\"mobility-transport-networks-1\",\"type\":\"mobility-transport-networks\",\"content\":{\"cardDescriptionColor\":\"#000000\",\"iconColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"titleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"cardTitleColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"transportNetworks\":[{\"title\":\"Rail & Transit\",\"description\":\"Modern rail and metro solutions designed for high-capacity movement, reliability and seamless urban connectivity.\",\"iconName\":\"route\"},{\"title\":\"Roads & Highways\",\"description\":\"Efficient expressways and arterial road networks engineered to improve flow, reduce congestion and enhance regional mobility.\",\"iconName\":\"map\"},{\"title\":\"Aviation\",\"description\":\"Master planning and infrastructure development for airports that prioritize safety, capacity and future-ready passenger experience.\",\"iconName\":\"activity\"},{\"title\":\"New Mobility\",\"description\":\"Integration of EV systems, micromobility, autonomous vehicles and next-generation mobility services into urban ecosystems.\",\"iconName\":\"layers\"},{\"title\":\"Maritime\",\"description\":\"Port, harbor and coastal infrastructure solutions supporting safe navigation, logistics efficiency and sustainable maritime operations.\",\"iconName\":\"zap\"},{\"title\":\"Tunnels\",\"description\":\"Advanced tunneling and underground mobility engineering for efficient, safe and resilient transportation routes.\",\"iconName\":\"map\"},{\"title\":\"Civil Structures\",\"description\":\"High-performance bridges, viaducts and structural systems designed for durability, safety and long-term public use.\",\"iconName\":\"radar\"},{\"title\":\"Parking Facilities\",\"description\":\"Smart, accessible parking systems optimized for capacity, safety and seamless integration with multimodal transport.\",\"iconName\":\"activity\"}],\"backgroundColor\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"backgroundGradientColor\":\"#EF4130\"}},{\"id\":\"mobility-vision-section\",\"type\":\"mobility-vision\",\"content\":{\"visionTitle\":\"Mobility today isn’t just about moving from point A to B—it’s about creating connected, adaptive, and intelligent systems that move people and goods effortlessly across evolving urban landscapes. By merging infrastructure design with smart technology, transport networks are reimagined as dynamic ecosystems—responsive to real-time needs, built for future growth, and centered around the human experience.\",\"visionPoints\":[{\"title\":\"Mobility-as-a-System\",\"description\":\"Designs that go beyond roads—integrating rail, EV, cycling, and pedestrian flows into one connected network.\"},{\"title\":\"Real-Time Intelligence\",\"description\":\"Data-driven platforms that monitor, predict, and optimize traffic, reducing delays and improving efficiency citywide.\"},{\"title\":\"Tech-First Infrastructure\",\"description\":\"Embedded sensors, adaptive lighting, smart intersections—built for today, ready for tomorrow.\"},{\"title\":\"Designing for Everyone\",\"description\":\"Inclusive planning that ensures mobility access for all ages, abilities, and modes of movement.\"}],\"visionImageUrl\":\"\",\"visionAccentColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"visionBackgroundColor\":\"#0f172a\",\"textColor\":\"#ffffff\"}},{\"id\":\"mobility-conclusion-1\",\"type\":\"mobility-conclusion\",\"content\":{\"textColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"accentColor\":\"#3B82F6\"}}]', '2025-11-28 12:51:17', 'raus@gmail.com', 0, NULL),
