-857268.jpg\"},{\"title\":\"Stakeholder Engagement Forums\",\"description\":\"Regular virtual and in-person workshops where partners, clients and communities share feedback and shape our growth roadmap.\",\"icon\":\"users\",\"backgroundImage\":\"https://jalgzgoha9oynfjc.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/image/1763382485320-414139.jpg\"},{\"title\":\"Governance Excellence Recognition\",\"description\":\"Annual awards celebrating teams that demonstrate exceptional transparency, responsibility and ethical conduct.\",\"icon\":\"award\",\"backgroundImage\":\"https://jalgzgoha9oynfjc.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/image/1763382497982-744278.jpg\"},{\"title\":\"Digital Governance Playbook\",\"description\":\"A living document that defines our governance philosophy — accessible, measurable and adaptable to evolving global standards.\",\"icon\":\"book\",\"backgroundImage\":\"https://jalgzgoha9oynfjc.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/image/1763382509531-497975.jpg\"}]}},{\"id\":\"our-values-editable-card-states\",\"type\":\"our-values-value-card-stats-card\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"\",\"subtitle\":\"Corporate governance is our promise of integrity, transparency and accountability. It’s the foundation that allows us to innovate boldly, partner responsibly and create long-term value for all.\",\"cardBorderColor\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"subtitleColor\":\"#000000\",\"columns\":{\"sm\":1,\"base\":1,\"md\":2,\"lg\":2,\"xl\":2},\"items\":[{\"value\":\"40%\",\"description\":\"of board materials distributed and signed off via a secure digital platform.\",\"title\":\"\",\"icon\":\"📁\",\"alignment\":\"left\"},{\"value\":\"60%\",\"description\":\"of risk assessments now leverage AI-driven scenario modeling to anticipate regulatory shifts.\",\"title\":\"\",\"icon\":\"🔍\",\"alignment\":\"left\"},{\"value\":\"25%\",\"description\":\"female representation among independent directors surpassing industry average by 10 %.\",\"title\":\"\",\"icon\":\"👩‍💼\",\"alignment\":\"left\"},{\"value\":\"7%\",\"descripti